  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559550/extras/Image.JPG?t=1733400433\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a small notebook, an abandoned character was drawn without any story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For a long time, the character lived lonely and trapped in the notebook, but one day, the character gathered courage and decided to escape the notebook.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid the various backgrounds drawn on the note and obstacles that hinder the character and advance towards the end of this note.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Gameplay</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are various backgrounds drawn on the note that look like they were drawn by a person. Climb up and avoid the background with simple but challenging controls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-Be prepared for the dangers of various traps!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many traps hidden throughout the beautiful-looking background that can hinder the characters. If you don't avoid the trap, there's no guarantee what the consequences will be...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-Choose where you land carefully!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All objects interact with the character. Find a place for your character to rest in the bouncy background!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● High risk, high return </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● All progress is automatically saved </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Repetitive play </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Various gimmicks that harass players </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Unique graphic background </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Simple operation </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559550/extras/b83f8eafa19bc764f218fe089b63d579.poster.avif?t=1733400433\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559550/extras/b83f8eafa19bc764f218fe089b63d579.webm?t=1733400433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559550/extras/b83f8eafa19bc764f218fe089b63d579.mp4?t=1733400433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i>Manipulation</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559550/extras/4b8bb31074708656c6a55d5d2c2c9b17.poster.avif?t=1733400433\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559550/extras/4b8bb31074708656c6a55d5d2c2c9b17.webm?t=1733400433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559550/extras/4b8bb31074708656c6a55d5d2c2c9b17.mp4?t=1733400433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i>Various gimmicks</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559550/extras/d94c6e53214739b16ad4ecb138de2485.poster.avif?t=1733400433\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559550/extras/d94c6e53214739b16ad4ecb138de2485.webm?t=1733400433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559550/extras/d94c6e53214739b16ad4ecb138de2485.mp4?t=1733400433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i>Interference Trap</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Game background</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel freely in a sketch-like background drawn on paper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Classic graphics </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Sketch-style background </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Smooth operation</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559550/extras/Image.JPG?t=1733400433\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a small notebook, an abandoned character was drawn without any story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For a long time, the character lived lonely and trapped in the notebook, but one day, the character gathered courage and decided to escape the notebook.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid the various backgrounds drawn on the note and obstacles that hinder the character and advance towards the end of this note.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Gameplay</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are various backgrounds drawn on the note that look like they were drawn by a person. Climb up and avoid the background with simple but challenging controls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-Be prepared for the dangers of various traps!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many traps hidden throughout the beautiful-looking background that can hinder the characters. If you don't avoid the trap, there's no guarantee what the consequences will be...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-Choose where you land carefully!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All objects interact with the character. Find a place for your character to rest in the bouncy background!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● High risk, high return </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● All progress is automatically saved </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Repetitive play </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Various gimmicks that harass players </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Unique graphic background </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Simple operation </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" 